# Price Fabric

## Tech Stack
Python, PricesAPI, Confluent Kafka, GitHub Actions, Microsoft Fabric (downstream).

## Code Style
`snake_case` for functions/variables, `PascalCase` for classes, strict type hints.

## Subagents
Delegate shell commands to the `shell` subagent; codebase search to `explore`.

## Fabric naming
Eventstream `es_prices_ingestion`; Bronze `raw_prices_stream`; Silver `silver_product_catalog`, `silver_price_history`; Gold `gold_competitor_gaps`, `gold_reliability_scores`.
